<br />
hmm, try a:
<br />
aptitude --purge-unused upgrade
<br />

<br />
in general, if you try to use aptitude, it has automatic removal of unused 
<br />
packages, every time you install, upgrade or remove something. Both 
<br />
command-line and gui are wonderful!
